&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Us:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At &lt;strong&gt;Bolo AI&lt;/strong&gt;, our mission is to use AI to make daily work faster, safer, and better for the heavy industry worker. We are building the next-generation agentic platform for heavy industries, starting with the Energy sector - enabling intelligent systems that reason, retrieve, and act across complex workflows spanning the field, office, and control center. We are an early-stage startup backed by True Ventures, Benchstrength, Accomplice, J Ventures, and Beat Ventures. We are a small team, which means the work is high-ownership, customer-facing, and close to the company’s core strategy. &lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We are AI-native: we use AI agents internally across every function, and we expect everyone on the team to work that way.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:200}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Overview:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;We’re hiring a &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Forward Deployed Product Manager&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt; to own customer engagement outcomes from problem discovery through shipped impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;This is not a traditional roadmap PM role, and it is not an implementation-only delivery role. You will sit at the intersection of customer, GTM, and engineering: understanding messy operational workflows, scoping the right MVP, translating customer needs into product requirements, and driving the engagement to measurable business value.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;The core skill is turning ambiguity into shipped outcomes. You will work with customers who have complex workflows, fragmented data, security constraints, and high expectations. Your job is to create clarity, sequence the work, manage tradeoffs, and make sure what we build is useful for the customer and reusable for Bolo.&amp;nbsp;For every customer engagement, especially pilots, the bar is not “did we deliver what we promised?” The bar is:&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;did we create so much value that the customer does not want to live without Bolo when the pilot ends?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt; This role is accountable for helping us reach that level of customer pull.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;You will be accountable for both customer success and product learning. That means you are not just delivering one-off customer requests. You are expected to identify repeatable patterns, shape product direction, and help us build scalable delivery processes as we grow.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Note: This role can be based in &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Palo Alto, CA or Houston, TX&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;. In either location, this is an in-person, customer-facing role. You should expect regular team collaboration, customer meetings, on-site discovery, and travel. Travel will vary by customer phase and may reach up to 50% during intensive discovery, deployment, or expansion periods.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Own:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own customer engagements from discovery through deployment, adoption, and measurable impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build credibility with customer stakeholders across field teams, technical teams, executives, and commercial buyers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Immerse yourself in the customer’s world through both their data and their day-to-day workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate messy customer problems into clear problem statements, MVP scope, data requirements, user stories, and product requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with engineering to turn customer workflows and datasets into stable, extensible AI-powered solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage tradeoffs across customer urgency, technical complexity, commercial value,

&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Software Engineer — AI-Native Full Stack&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bolo.ai&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bay Area (Hybrid) | Salt Lake City Area (Remote) | Full-Time Senior Engineer&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role Has Changed&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Three person engineering teams are building what used to take thirty. Not by working harder, but by working differently. The engineers shipping at this pace don&#39;t write code. They write specs precise enough that agents implement them correctly. They build harnesses. CI gates, structural tests, linting rules, and architectural enforcement that mechanically prevent entire classes of agent mistakes. They design validation systems where agents write the tests and humans verify that features actually work from the user&#39;s perspective.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The code is a generated artifact. The spec, the harness, and the validation infrastructure are what engineers maintain.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is how we work at Bolo.ai. We&#39;re hiring engineers who already work this way, or who have the depth to start.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Company&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bolo.ai builds generative AI systems for the energy industry, making daily work faster, safer, and better for heavy industry workers. We have Fortune 500 contracts, production deployments, and growing enterprise demand. We&#39;re scaling.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Energy adds real constraints. Regulatory compliance, data residency, operational technology integration, deployment across cloud and on-premises infrastructure. These constraints make the architecture harder and the work more interesting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Work&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll spend your time on four things:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications. &lt;/strong&gt;You write behavioral specs, architectural constraints, and feature requirements that agents implement against. When agent output misses the mark, you tighten the spec. Not by adding more words, but by being more precise about what &quot;correct&quot; means. This requires understanding the system deeply enough to define its behavior at every layer.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Harness. &lt;/strong&gt;You build and maintain the infrastructure that keeps agents producing reliable code. Structural tests that enforce architectural boundaries. Linting rules where every failure message teaches the agent what went wrong. CI gates that reject drift. Structured knowledge bases agents can navigate. The principle: every class of agent mistake gets a mechanical fix so it never recurs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Validation. &lt;/strong&gt;Agents write the code. Agents write the tests. You verify that features work from the user&#39;s perspective, under real deployment conditions, against edge cases that matter in production. You define scenarios and acceptance criteria. You build the end-to-end checks,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;behavioral verification, and automation that make this trustworthy at scale. When something breaks, your job is diagnosing whether the failure is in the spec, the harness, or the agent&#39;s implementation, and fixing the right layer.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Architecture and operations. &lt;/strong&gt;Our systems run across cloud providers and on-premises environments. You design modular abstractions, clean interfaces where deployment targets don&#39;t leak into application logic. You own production systems used by energy companies in regulated environments where failures have real consequences. Reliability, observability, and graceful degradation matter here.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Makes Someone Good at This&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;7+

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Hybrid&amp;nbsp; •&amp;nbsp; Full-Time&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:300}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;heading 2&quot;&gt;About Bolo AI&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:280,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Bolo AI is building the next-generation&amp;nbsp;AI&amp;nbsp;agentic platform for heavy industries&amp;nbsp;to make them faster, safer, and better.&amp;nbsp;We create an intelligent context layer across complex industrial data, enabling AI&amp;nbsp;agents&amp;nbsp;that reason, retrieve, and act across workflows spanning the field, office, and control center. Our customers include energy companies, utilities, refineries, and chemical operators who use our platform to replace weeks of manual analysis with intelligent systems that surface what matters.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:200}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Our early customers are seeing&amp;nbsp;real results&amp;nbsp;— from catching critical equipment failures hiding in plain sight to automating production optimization workflows that were previously done in spreadsheets.&amp;nbsp;We are a small team backed by True Ventures,&amp;nbsp;Benchstrength, Accomplice, Analog Ventures, and Beat Ventures.&amp;nbsp;We are AI-native: we use AI agents internally across every function, and we expect everyone on the team to work that way.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:200}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;heading 2&quot;&gt;The Role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:280,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We are hiring a Strategic Account Executive to own the full sales cycle,&amp;nbsp;from generating&amp;nbsp;pipeline&amp;nbsp;to closing enterprise deals across the energy and industrial sector. You will work directly with the founder and founding team, shaping both the deals we pursue and the sales motion we build.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:200}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;This is the part of a company’s journey that defines what comes next&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;which industries we expand into, how we sell, and what repeatable growth looks like. You will source your own opportunities through events,&amp;nbsp;outbound, channel partners, and your network. You will build custom demos on real customer data, manage pilots hands-on, and close. The work you do here will compound: the deals, the playbook, and the relationships you build will shape Bolo AI for years. The role requires regular travel for customer meetings, pilots, and industry events.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:200}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
